description:
Quickfire Method to find Square Roots and Cube Roots of Perfect Squares /Perfect Cubes of numbers up to 100.

This course teaches you a new method to find squares of numbers ending with '5'.

And also teaches the amazing method of finding Square Roots and Cube Roots of Perfect Squares /Perfect Cubes of numbers up to 100.

Its simple to learn. Much simpler to practice. And Simplest to impress others.

This course is helpful for competitive exams like SAT, GRE, GMAT, CAT, MBA entrance etc.
title: Quickfire Method 2 find Square Roots & Cube Roots of Numbers
